credit.credit-words: The Book of Psalms for Singing
The great salvation wrought by Him Jehovah has made known. His justice in the nations’ sight He openly has shown.
He mindful of His grace and truth To Israel’s house has been, The great salvation of our God All ends of earth have seen.
With harp make music to the L
; With harp, a psalm O sing!
With horn and trumpet raise a shout Before the L
Let seas in all their vastness roar, The world, its living horde.
Let rivers clap, let mountains sing Their joy
7. Because He comes, He surely comes, The judge of earth to be! With justice He will judge the world, All men with equity.
